OL,3,CSilvertown tunnel reduces congestion
OL,4,Cin its first year says TfL
OL,6,FA year after opening, Transport for
OL,7,FLondon says the Silvertown Tunnel is
OL,8,Fcutting congestion and improving air
OL,9,Fquality.
OL,11,FA new report by TfL shows peak journey
OL,12,Ftimes at the Blackwall Tunnel were
OL,13,Falmost 60% faster northbound.
OL,15,FThe report found that cross river bus
OL,16,Fjourneys have increased by 290%.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
