OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784843302
OL,3,CSilvertown tunnel reduces congestion
OL,4,Cin its first year says TfL
OL,6,FMonitoring also revealed that nitrogen
OL,7,Fdioxide concentrations have decreased
OL,8,Fby 17% on average, compared to the
OL,9,Fyear before the tunnel opened- helping
OL,10,FLondoners to breathe cleaner air.
OL,12,FThe 1.4km toll tunnel links Silvertown
OL,13,Fand the Greenwich Peninsula in east
OL,14,FLondon.
OL,16,FDesigned to ease pressure on the
OL,17,FBlackwall Tunnel, the road opened in
OL,18,FApril 2025
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
