OL,3,CSilvertown tunnel reduces congestion
OL,4,Cin its first year says TfL
OL,6,FIt is the first new road Thames
OL,7,Fcrossing east of London's Tower Bridge
OL,8,Fin 33 years.
OL,10,FMayor of London, Sadiq Khan, said:
OL,12,F"This analysis shows that the
OL,13,FSilvertown Tunnel is proving a
OL,14,Fsuccess, not only cutting journey
OL,15,Ftimes but encouraging more sustainable
OL,16,Ftransport so we can keep cleaning up
OL,17,Four air.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
