FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784843302
OL,3,CSilvertown tunnel reduces congestion
OL,4,Cin its first year says TfL
OL,6,F"I'm particularly pleased to see major
OL,7,Freductions in congestion at the
OL,8,FBlackwall Tunnel benefitting
OL,9,Fbusinesses and local residents.
OL,11,F"The Silvertown Tunnel is already
OL,12,Ftransforming travel across the Thames
OL,13,Fas we continue building a greener,
OL,14,Ffairer, better London for everyone."
OL,16,FConcerns were raised about the
OL,17,FSilvertown Tunnel before it opened
OL,18,Faround pollution and congestion.
OL,26,@vD@dO]
