PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784843302
OL,3,CSilvertown tunnel reduces congestion
OL,4,Cin its first year says TfL
OL,6,FIt is also the first road access
OL,7,Fcharging in London since the
OL,8,Fcongestion charge in 2003.
OL,10,FThe money used to build the tunnel is
OL,11,Fbeing paid back with tolls over 25
OL,12,Fyears, although there are some
OL,13,Fexemptions including blue badge
OL,14,Fholders and black cabs.
OL,16,FAlex Williams, Chief Customer and
OL,17,FStrategy Officer at TfL, said that the
OL,18,Ftunnel has been successful in
OL,19,F"improving the resilience of the road
OL,20,Fnetwork and reducing congestion, with
OL,21,Fimproving air quality." She continued:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
