OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1784843302
OL,3,CSilvertown tunnel reduces congestion
OL,4,Cin its first year says TfL
OL,6,F"By making it easier to travel by bus
OL,7,Facross and near the river, we're also
OL,8,Fseeing a surge in customers choosing
OL,9,Fto travel more sustainably.
OL,11,F"With more reliable journeys, improved
OL,12,Faccess to public transport and reduced
OL,13,Femissions, the tunnel is delivering
OL,14,Freal benefits for people and
OL,15,Fbusinesses on both sides of the river."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/6
